@73102  = ~Forest Druid~
@73103  = ~FOREST DRUID: Forest Druids reside in the regions where soil is nutritious, plant life is abundant and animals thrive. Tall forests are a paradise in many ways: they provide shade from the sun, food and homes for animals and people, and wood for tools. While other wildlands can be wondrous escapes, forests are incessantly under threat of being torn down and subjugated by careless humans and demihumans. Forest druids therefore often live with a constant low-grade paranoia, which informs the stereotype of druids being hostile to civilization.

